ant\/","url_meta":{"origin":3487,"position":2},"title":"Ali on Justice: Treat others as you want to be treated","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 25, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Asakir reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever desires to be fair to people, let him love for them as he loves for himself.\u201d Source:\u00a0Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 44955 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0633\u0627\u0643\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064c \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0635\u0650\u0641\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0633\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064f\u062d\u0650\u0628\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24651,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/04\/09\/ali-on-justice-scale-between\/","url_meta":{"origin":3487,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Justice: Make a scale between you and others","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Muttaqi al-Hindi reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cMake yourself a scale between you and others. Love for those besides you what you love for yourself, and hate for them what you hate for yourself. Do not wrong others, as you would love not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0